<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Features - Express App</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <header class="feature-header">
    <h1>🚀 App Features</h1>
    <p>Explore the powerful capabilities of our Express.js application.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="features-grid">
    <article class="feature-item">
      <div class="icon">🧠</div>
      <h2>Dynamic Rendering</h2>
      <p>Render personalized content using EJS templates for each user.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-item">
      <div class="icon">🧭</div>
      <h2>Multiple Routes</h2>
      <p>Efficiently handle multiple pages like Home, About, and Features.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-item">
      <div class="icon">📁</div>
