      <p>Serve CSS, JS, and images directly from the `public` folder.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="feature-item">
      <div class="icon">⚙️</div>
      <h2>Templating Engine</h2>
      <p>Use EJS to generate reusable, server-rendered components.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
